<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-11-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-11-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="1573" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1573">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 012/3749.</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Consular Agent <persName type="from">Glenn</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                        State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Guanajuato</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-16">
                                        <hi rend="italic">November 16, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I would thank you to kindly advise me
                                your wishes as regards Spanish religious institutions and Spaniards
                                in general. There is no Spanish Consul in this State and I have had
                                very many requests <pb facs="1164" n="1048" xml:id="pg_1048"/> from
                                Spaniards for assistance, they claiming that in Guadalajara and
                                other parts they are under the protection of the American flag.</p>
                            <p>Awaiting [etc.]</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">John B. Glenn.</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>